title: Mississippi State tries to get back in West race vs Kentucky (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,466 Mississippi State tries to get back in West race vs Kentucky (Yahoo Sports) Mississippi State already has two losses against conference opponents, putting a serious dent in the program's hope of winning a SEC Western Division title. Mississippi State (5-2, 1-2 SEC) gets a chance to inch up the league standings on Saturday when it hosts Kentucky (4-2, 2-2). The Bulldogs have won six straight games in the series, though most have been close.
